    "body": "It'd also be nice if we could build grpc from source in Alpine.  I use an Alpine-based docker image for CI and just noticed that it doesn't build with musl libc (`sched_getcpu` isn't implemented in Alpine 3.4's musl libc; musl master does appear to have at least a prototype for it though...).\n\nI guess I'll have to switch to a glibc based distro for now (up to this point I was building a very lightweight docker image for demoing the product too, something not possible with other distros ðŸ˜¢ ).\n"
  },
